    "body": "Thats kind of interesting. A Nodes response asks for a specific distance, and I'd expect you should just grab all the nodes in your bucket. A bucket should have a max of 16 peers. It's surprising that you store more peers than that for any given distance.\r\n\r\nEDIT: Just looked at the PR, its a sync issue. Makes sense",
